SCREEN Keybinding

Creating Window 	C-a c
Switching windows 	C-a n
Listing Windows		C-a w	C-a "
Toggle between current	C-a C-a
and previous windwos
start copy mode		C-a [
paste copied text	C-a ]
Enter title for windows	C-a A
Detaching Window	C-a d
Reattach window		screen -r 
Logging sreen		C-a H
Stopping screen		C-a k


SPLIT

horizontally 		C-a S
vertically		C-a | || C-a V
Jump to next display 	C-a tab
remove current region	C-a X
remove all region expt	C-a Q
current


redraw Window		C-a C-l
Getting alerts		C-a M
Locking screen session	C-a x
enter screen command 	C-a :
